# Local environment pointer (repository root)
# Copy this file to `.env.local` or merge into `.env` — never commit real secrets.
#
# Full variable catalog (required + optional profiles): see repo root `.env.example`.
# Canonical environment catalog: repo root .env.example
#
# Quick start:
#   cp .env.example .env
#   # edit .env with your keys; optional: keep machine-specific overrides in .env.local
#
# Vite apps may still use `frontend/.env.example` or `apps/data-management-frontend/.env.example`
# for SPA-only `VITE_*` overrides; those files also point at the root catalog.
